<div style="margin-bottom:20px; margin-left:50px; margin-right:50px; margin-top:100px">
<h1>RULES OF THE<br />
BWT 2020 &quot;SUMMER OF EXCELLENCE&quot; DRAW<br />
TO BE HELD IN STORE</h1>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 1: ORGANISATION OF THE DRAW</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">PROCOPI (member of the BWT Group) , a French simplified joint stock company, with a share capital of &euro; 7,000,000.00, whose registered office is situate in les landes d&rsquo;Apign&eacute; &ndash; 35 650 LE RHEU, France, registered with&nbsp; the Paris Trade and Companies register under the number 333 263 846 (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Organising Company&quot;) is organising, between June the 1st (as of 10:00 am) and the 30th of September 2020 (up to 11:59 pm) inclusive, GMT+1,&nbsp; a draw with obligation to purchase , entitled BWT 2020 &quot;Summer of Excellence&quot;.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The draw is open to all persons of legal age</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">residing in mainland France (including Corsica), Belgium, Luxembourg and the Netherlands, not including employees of the Organising Company or any of its affiliated companies. Only one prize will be awarded per participant. Participation in the Draw shall be construed as acceptance by the participant of these rules and the principal of the Draw, without any reservations. Any person found to be in breach of one or more articles set out herein shall be deprived of participation in the Draw, and also any prize that they may have won.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 2 : ANNOUNCEMENT OF THE GAME</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">This Draw is hosted on the internet site <a href="http://www.summerbwt.fr" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">www.summerbwt.fr</a></span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:#212529">The PHARE-WEST agency has been appointed to organise the Draw in the name of and on behalf of the Organising Company. The PHARE-WEST agency and PROCOPI (member of the BWT Group) shall be referred to together as &quot;the Organisers&quot;.</span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 3 : CONDITIONS GOVERNING PARTICIPATION IN THE DRAW</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">This Game, predicated on a purchase, is hosted solely on the internet site www.summerbwt.fr belonging to PROCOPI (member of the BWT group) between June the 1st (as of 10:00 am) and the 30th of September 2020 (up to 11:59 pm) inclusive, GMT +1, inclusive. Participation in the Draw is reserved to physical persons over 18 years of age, residing in France, Belgium, Luxembourg or the Netherlands (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;Participants&quot;), with the exception of employees of the Organising Companies, affiliated companies, companies partnering the Operation, as well as members of their families and any persons who took part in the elaboration of the Draw. In the event of a discrepancy or dispute, proof of identity may be requested.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">It is hereby expressly recalled that the participant must have access to an internet connection and a valid e-ail address in order to participate in the draw.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">To participate in the draw:</span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">1. Purchase a product from the BWT Pool Chemicals range in a participating store (a list of participating stores is available on the internet site <a href="http://www.summerbwt.fr" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">www.summerbwt.fr</a>)</span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">2. Create your account on the internet site <a href="http://www.summerbwt.fr" style="color:#0563c1; text-decoration:underline">www.summerbwt.fr</a></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:#212529">3. Click on &quot;Try your luck&quot; in the &quot;Pool chemical draw&quot; space.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">4. Upload your proof(s) of purchase and indicate the store in which the BWT pool chemicals were purchased.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">5. Select the country in which the pool chemicals were purchased. </span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">6. Select the store in which the pool chemicals were purchased.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:#212529">A first e-mail confirming participation subject to verification of the proof(s) of purchase will be sent to the participant.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">A second e-mail confirming registration for the draw will be sent to the participant. In the event that multiple purchases of BWT pool chemicals are made during the peiod of the validity of the draw, the participant should reconnect&nbsp; to the internet site summerbwt.fr for each subsequent purchase in order to validate the purchase and multiply their entries into the draw. The more purchases of BWT water treatment products the participant makes, the more chances that they will have of winning.</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:#212529"> Illegible, incomplete, unintelligible entries, or entries found to be anomalous or fraudulent shall not be taken into consideration.</span></span></span></p>

<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:#212529">Only winners of a 3 day pass for a European F1 Grand Prix 2020 or 2021 season (European Grand Prix to be defined in relation with the official F1 calendar evolution) will be contacted by the Phase-West agency within approximately 10 days following the date of the draw, winners of other prizes will be notified within 6 weeks. The Organisers shall not be held responsible on any grounds whatsoever for malfunctions associated with telephone and/or internet networks and connections, or for any other issues that may arise while the Draw is being run, or for the rescheduling and/ or cancellation and/ or the modification of the Draw for reasons beyond their control. The organisers shall notably not be held responsible if fields filled in by the participants do not reach them, or are illegible or impossible to process for whatever reason whatsoever. The organisers shall not be held responsible for delays or errors in transmission of e-mails or post that lie beyond their control and hereby decline all responsibility in the event of an incident or incorrect use of the computer and/ or communication network.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 4: DESCRIPTION AND VALUE OF THE PRIZES</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">For the BWT 2020 &quot;Summer of Excellence&quot; draw, each participating store will have:</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">-3 day pass for 1 person for a European Formula 1 Grand Prix (to be defined in relation with the official F1 calendar evolution), with an estimated unit value of &euro;170 after tax - </span>transport not included.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">- BWT promotional goodies and textiles (depending on available stocks) with an estimated total value of&nbsp; &euro; 20&nbsp; after tax.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 5: METHOD FOR DESIGNATING WINNERS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Prizes offered will be allocated in accordance with the principals of a draw.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The draw will be held on the 12th of October 2020 and there will be 2 winners per store (in stores participating in the operation) drawn from participants who purchased one or more BWT pool chemical products in a participating store. The first person drawn shall win the 3 day pass for 1 person for a European Formula 1 Grand Prix (to be defined in relation with the official F1 calendar evolution). The second person drawn will win the BWT promotional goodies and/ or textiles (depending on available stocks).</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 6 : MODALITES D</span></span></strong><strong><span dir="RTL" lang="AR-SA" style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">&rsquo;</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ATTRIBUTION DES LOTS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Winners shall receive their prize in the store in which their purchase was made, said store havinf participated in the Summer of Excellence operation, before the 26th of October 2020. Only one prize will be allocated per household (same name and/or postal address and/or e-mail address). In the event of a discrepancy or dispute, proof of identity and/ or address may be requested. Photos of the prizes that may be handed out are not contractually binding. Prizes awarded to the winners may not give rise to any dispute whatsoever, nor to the award of the equivalent value in money (either total or partial), nor may they be exchanged or substituted on any grounds whatsoever. Consequently, no claims of any kind will be entertained. The organisers shall not bear any contractual responsibility concerning the proper running, use, compliance with standards to which the prizes may be subject nor for the safety of the prizes awarded. The organisers hereby decline all responsibility for any dissatisfaction the winner may experience concerning their prize.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Should circumstances require, the organisers reserve the right to alter the type of prize and offer a prize of the same value or same type.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The participants hereby authorise all verification of their identity and domicile required for the organisers to ensure the participants&#39; adherence to the rules set out herein. Requests for proof of a participant&#39;s identity or domicile will be addressed to the participant by the organisers in writing.</span></span> </span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Any erroneous or incomplete registrations shall be considered void. Details that are incomplete, fraudulent or provided in a manner that contradicts the rules set out herein shall entail the disqualification of the participant and cancellation of their participation and any winnings. In the event of disqualification of a winner, the latter shall be deprived of all rights under the terms of these rules and notably those concerning receiving the prizes offered.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 7 - FORCE MAJEURE</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The organisers hereby reserve the right to shorten, extend, modify postpone or cancel the draw should circumstances require, and notably on the grounds of an event beyond their control or in case of Force Majeure, without their liability being engaged.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 8 - CONNECTION AND COMMUNICATION</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">It is hereby expressly recalled that participation in the draw shall be construed as knowledge of and acceptance of the characteristics and limitations of the telephony and internet operators&#39; communication networks, particularly with regard to risks of interruption, technical performance, response times required to view, query or transfer data or documents, the lack of protection against possible diversion of some data, and risks of contamination by viruses that may be circulating on the internet.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The organisers shall not be held liable on any grounds whatsoever for malfunctions associated with telephone and/ or internet connections, or for any other issue that may arise throughout the period of this draw, nor shall they be held liable for the postponement and/ or cancellation and/ or modification of the draw on grounds that are beyond their control, more specifically in the event that a participant cannot log in to their client account on PROCOPI (member of the BWT group) &#39;s internet site www.summerbwt.fr , due to technical problems notably those associated with network saturation. Any interrupted connection shall be considered not to have taken place.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The organisers shall do their utmost to provide users with available and verified information and/ or tools, but shall not be held liable for errors for the lack of availability of information.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The organisers shall not be held liable for any material or immaterial damage caused to participants, to their computer equipment or the data stored therein, or for any direct or indirect consequences&nbsp; that may ensue.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 9 &ndash; CONNECTION COSTS</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Costs of participation in the draw shall not be reimbursed.</span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 10: ADVERTISING AND PROMOTION OF THE WINNER</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">By simply participating in the draw, the participants hereby accept, in the event that they are designated a winner, to allow the Organising Companies, or any person appointed by the Organising Companies for this purpose, to capture their image without being entitled to any remuneration other than the Prize won or to any other compensation, and hereby expressly authorise the Organising Companies to use the images captured on this occasion to communicate about the Draw or the results of the latter, for a period of one year as of the date of the e-mail advising them of their win and on any media support, notably the internet, and this, throughout the world.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Similarly, the Participants hereby accept that the Organising Companies may, for advertising purposes, cite their surname, first name and their city of residence without restrictions or reservations, and without the Participants being entitled to any remuneration, rights or any other advantage other than the allocation of their prize.</span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white">&nbsp;</span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 11 - PROTECTION OF PERSONAL DATA</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">In order to participate in the draw, the participant must impart some of their personal data (surname, first name, e-mail address, home address, telephone number). This data is required to determine the winners and allocate and convey prizes. The aforementioned data, saved in an electronic file, is intended only for the organisers who will use it solely for this purpose.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Data will be retained for two months, with the exception of data, the minimum retention period of which would give rise to a legal or regulatory obligation or the suppression of the limitation period. </span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The participant may avail themselves of their rights and request access to their data, the correction or deletion of data,&nbsp; the transfer of data to third parties, the transmission of data in the event of death, the limitation of processing and opposition to processing by sending a request in writing to the following address:</span></span><br />
<br />
<strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="color:black">PhareWest-SummerBWT<br />
BP 35<br />
92310 SEVRES FRANCE</span></span></strong></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Any requests should be clear and precise, justified, and must be accompanied by a copy of a proof of identity.<br />
Where the objection is justified, or in the event that the data is erroneous or misleading, as the services involved in gathering the data may not be made public, the organising company hereby declines responsibility on these grounds.</span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 12: MODIFICATION OF THE RULES</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The rules of the game are deposited with SELARL ACTA - PIERSON and ASSOCIATES holder of a judicial office domiciled at 15 rue de Sarre BP 15126 57074 METZ Cedex 3.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">The Organising Companies hereby reserve the right to amend the articles set out hereto and notably the rules of the Draw and the prizes awarded. Every modification shall be recorded in an amendment filed with the judicial officer SELARL ACTA - PIERSON et ASSOCIES holder of a judicial office domiciled at the 15 rue de Sarre BP 15126 57074 METZ Cedex 3, similarly to the regulations set out hereto. Any modification to the regulations will form the subject of an amendment and communication to the participants.</span></span></span></span></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><strong><span style="font-size:16.0pt"><span style="color:black">ARTICLE 13 - INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="background-color:white"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="color:black">Images and/ or photographs featured on the internet site of the draw, www.summerbwt.fr, are the sole property of the Organising Company. Any copying and/ or use is strictly prohibited.</span></span>&nbsp;</span></span></p>

